File Create-Read-Write

	Create a file => touch file_name
	Read a file => cat file_name
	Wirte to file => nano file_name
	
	

Archieving 

	Extract file => tar -xzvf file_name.tar.gz
	Extract to other dir => tar -xzvf file_name.tar.gz -C destination_directory/
	Compress File => tar -czf file1 file2 folder1 folder2 folder3



Fiel Permission (Read r , Write w , Execute x )

	Allow read permission => chmod +r file_name
	Allow write permission => chmod +w file_name
	Allow execute permission => chmod +x file_name

	Disallow read permission => chmod -r file_name
	Disallow write permission => chmod -w file_name
	Disallow execute persmission => chmod -x file_name
	
	

File copy,cut
	
	Copy a file => cp source_directory destination_directory
	Cut a file => mv source_directory destination_directory
	
	
	
Installation

	Add repository => sudo add-apt-repository <ppa_repository>
	Installation => sudo apt install git (OR) sudo apt-get install git
	Uninstallation => sudo apt remove git (OR) sudo apt --purge remove git
	Fix broken install => sudo apt --fix-broken install
